CARE: Camera and Readout

Simulation of the Camera and readout of a Cherenkov Telescope

make 

execute with

./CameraAndReadout 4357 CARE.cfg output pixel.root

where:
4357                                          is the random number seed
CARE.cfg                          that is the config file for the CARE simulation
output                                        base name of the output files
pixel.root                                    name of the input file
